  "detailed_description": "The game \"Iceline\" is the story of the Ice Magician, who collects magic crystals and takes his skills to the next level. <br>This is a puzzle game with unique mechanics in which the player character leaves an ice trail behind him and thus changes the playing field for himself!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/5c6eaa4741d5d5d4506269bf09f909e6.poster.avif?t=1674550721\" width=702 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/5c6eaa4741d5d5d4506269bf09f909e6.webm?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/5c6eaa4741d5d5d4506269bf09f909e6.mp4?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The mage encounters obstacles in the form of walls, rocks, or ice trails on his path. <br>When the mage crosses an ice trail, his mana gains the ability to overcome any obstacle!<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/49bbae2801d2b5ac536d9ecc7e1524e3.poster.avif?t=1674550721\" width=702 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/49bbae2801d2b5ac536d9ecc7e1524e3.webm?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/49bbae2801d2b5ac536d9ecc7e1524e3.mp4?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In later levels, different colors of ice appear and this leads to some truly incredible logical challenges!<br>Each game level is a puzzle with its own logical solution. <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/2ec2c9b90e0616c164570f3491997976.poster.avif?t=1674550721\" width=702 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/2ec2c9b90e0616c164570f3491997976.webm?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/2ec2c9b90e0616c164570f3491997976.mp4?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br>- A unique puzzle mechanic where the player modifies the playing field.<br>- 50 levels of increasing difficulty.<br>- Intuitive game rules, which, however, will make you think in the final levels!<br>- Neat, clear puzzle graphics -- nothing unnecessary!<br>- Play at your own pace.<br>- Thrilling, but not annoying music will accompany you throughout the game!",
  "about_the_game": "The game \"Iceline\" is the story of the Ice Magician, who collects magic crystals and takes his skills to the next level. <br>This is a puzzle game with unique mechanics in which the player character leaves an ice trail behind him and thus changes the playing field for himself!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/5c6eaa4741d5d5d4506269bf09f909e6.poster.avif?t=1674550721\" width=702 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/5c6eaa4741d5d5d4506269bf09f909e6.webm?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/5c6eaa4741d5d5d4506269bf09f909e6.mp4?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The mage encounters obstacles in the form of walls, rocks, or ice trails on his path. <br>When the mage crosses an ice trail, his mana gains the ability to overcome any obstacle!<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/49bbae2801d2b5ac536d9ecc7e1524e3.poster.avif?t=1674550721\" width=702 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/49bbae2801d2b5ac536d9ecc7e1524e3.webm?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/49bbae2801d2b5ac536d9ecc7e1524e3.mp4?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In later levels, different colors of ice appear and this leads to some truly incredible logical challenges!<br>Each game level is a puzzle with its own logical solution. <br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/2ec2c9b90e0616c164570f3491997976.poster.avif?t=1674550721\" width=702 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/2ec2c9b90e0616c164570f3491997976.webm?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2157860/extras/2ec2c9b90e0616c164570f3491997976.mp4?t=1674550721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br>- A unique puzzle mechanic where the player modifies the playing field.<br>- 50 levels of increasing difficulty.<br>- Intuitive game rules, which, however, will make you think in the final levels!<br>- Neat, clear puzzle graphics -- nothing unnecessary!<br>- Play at your own pace.<br>- Thrilling, but not annoying music will accompany you throughout the game!",
